Yeah, but does he have what it takes?

537
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:38,170
等他拿出媒体方案就知道了
We'll see when I get his media plan.

538
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:40,300
他个性如何
What about his personality?

539
00:26:40,930 --> 00:26:44,690
迷人  直接  思维缜密
Charming. Direct. Very thorough.

540
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:48,470
