该死  我忘了马上要和销售部门开会
Shit. I forgot there's a meeting with sales in a couple minutes.

578
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:33,720
你想晚点继续吗
You want to do this later?

579
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,890
不用  我现在跑过去 
No. I'll just run over

580
00:28:34,890 --> 00:28:37,000
跟他们说我要晚几分钟到  马上回来
and let them know I'll be a few minutes late. Be right back.

581
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:38,440
好  我就在这儿
Cool. I'll be here.

582
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,200
好的
Okay.

583
00:28:55,970 --> 00:28:57,350
快点快点
Come on, come on, come on, come on.

584
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:03,170
来了
There.

585
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,700
快回复啊
Come on.

586
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,040
好
Okay.

587
00:29:32,720 --> 00:29:33,460
好嘞
Go.

588
00:29:36,870 --> 00:29:37,960
出什么事了
Something wrong?

589
00:29:38,090 --> 00:29:39,580
我找不着手机了  真奇怪
Can't find my phone. It -- it's weird.

590
00:29:39,580 --> 00:29:41,110
刚刚还在的
I had it just a minute ago.

591
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,170
找到了  不好意思
Here it is. Sorry about that.

592
00:29:50,170 --> 00:29:51,240
没事
No problem.

593
00:29:51,470 --> 00:29:54,210
那个多层体系结构
So the, uh, N-tier architecture.

594
00:29:54,210 --> 00:29:56,600
我刚说的那个高科技三明治
The high-tech sandwich I was talking about.

595
00:29:56,810 --> 00:29:58,710
我以为门多萨愿意合作
I thought Mendoza was willing to work with us.

596
00:29:58,710 --> 00:30:01,130
他是愿意  问题在柯蒂斯·哈斯
He is. The problem is Curtis Haas.

597
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,210
你跟他谈过了吗
And have you spoken with him?

598
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:05,280
他办公室不回我们电话
His office isn't returning our calls.

599
00:30:05,290 --> 00:30:06,220
门多萨也是
Neither is Mendoza's --

600
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:07,580
我不该让步的
I should've stuck to my guns.

601
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:10,630
明天下午才开始投票
The vote isn't until tomorrow afternoon.

602
00:30:10,630 --> 00:30:12,160
我一早就会联系门多萨
I'll reach out to Mendoza first thing in the --

603
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:14,330
这可是国情咨文  弗兰克
This is the State of the Union, Frank.

604
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:16,450
我不能陷入尴尬境地
I won't be left in limbo.

605
00:30:17,770 --> 00:30:19,620
如果我们得重写演讲
If we need to start rewriting that speech now,

606
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:21,140
我一分钟也不想耽误
I don't want to waste a minute.

607
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:23,360
我能扭转局面  先生
I can turn this around, sir.

608
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:26,050
雷蒙德告诉我这是你的点子
You know, Raymond told me this was your idea.

609
00:30:26,150 --> 00:30:27,860
做出妥协
To pursue this compromise.

610
00:30:27,860 --> 00:30:30,010
只是提出建议
I suggested it as an option.

611
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:31,630
他说是你逼他蹚这浑水的
He said you bullied him into it,

612
00:30:31,630 --> 00:30:34,030
他认为这是个错误的决定
that he thought it was a -- a mistake.

613
00:30:35,150 --> 00:30:38,740
如果他这么反对  他就应该劝阻你
If he felt so strongly, he should have advised you otherwise.

614
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:40,270
雷蒙德不是政客
Raymond is not a politician.

615
00:30:40,270 --> 00:30:42,260
他依赖于我们的政治意见
He relies on our political expertise

616
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:44,330
正如我们依靠他的商业头脑
as much as we rely on his business acumen.

617
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:47,120
或许我们应该到真出现问题再相互指责
Maybe we shouldn't point fingers until there's a problem.

618
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,550
你管这不叫问题
Oh, you wouldn't call this a problem.

619
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:51,030
在成为问题之前解决掉就不是问题
Not if it's solved before it becomes one.

620
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:57,020
我要的是个能管理好国会的副总统
You see, I wanted a Vice President who can manage Congress.

621
00:30:57,050 --> 00:30:59,210
而不是个不自量力的人
Not one who bites off more than he can chew.

622
00:30:59,210 --> 00:31:01,430
那就相信您做出了正确的决定  先生
Then have faith you made the right choice, sir.

623
00:31:01,430 --> 00:31:05,220
我的信念正在迅速地消失殆尽
Whatever faith I have is quickly evaporating.

624
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:08,280
别给政府丢脸  弗兰克
Don't humiliate the administration, Frank.

625
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,170
你也是其中一员了
You're part of it now.

626
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,430
是  先生
Yes, sir.

627
00:31:12,750 --> 00:31:13,780
我们谈完了
We're done.

628
00:31:14,490 --> 00:31:15,950
谢谢  总统先生
Thank you, Mr. President.

629
00:31:22,930 --> 00:31:24,430
帮我接内线
Give me the private line, please.

630
00:31:24,820 --> 00:31:28,110
塔斯克挡我道  古德温对我穷追不舍
Tusk is blocking my way. Goodwin at my heels.

631
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:30,110
现在一步也不能错
There can be no false steps now.

632
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:33,170
越往上爬  尔虞我诈越多
The higher up the mountain, the more treacherous the path.

633
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:36,400
卢卡斯·古德温去找她了
Lucas Goodwin went up to visit her.

634
00:31:37,130 --> 00:31:38,580
他们可能也会来找你
They may be looking for you.

635
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:41,320
没人找过我  应该没人知道我在这儿
Nobody's contacted me. I don't think anyone knows I'm here.

636
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:43,270
那我们要确保你不会被人发现
Then we need to make sure it stays that way.

637
00:31:43,620 --> 00:31:45,440
避免不必要的交谈
Don't speak to anyone you don't have to.

638
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,150
不要去不必要的地方
Don't go anywhere you don't need to be.

639
00:31:49,850 --> 00:31:51,020
告诉我你听到我说的了
Tell me you heard what I said.

640
00:31:51,020 --> 00:31:52,710
听到了  我知道了
I heard you. I get it.

641
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,340
我没事
I'm fine.

642
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,820
-敷点冰  -我说了我没事
- Put some ice on it. - I said it's okay.

643
00:32:41,150 --> 00:32:42,200
这是什么
What is this?

644
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:45,150
你现在还翻我的垃圾吗
What, are you going through my garbage now?

645
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:50,220
在公交上别人给我的
Someone gave it to me on the bus.

646
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:03,860
有人联系你  就来告诉我
You let me know if anyone contacts you.

647
00:33:39,570 --> 00:33:40,690
抱歉我来晚了
Sorry I'm late.

648
00:33:40,690 --> 00:33:41,690
没事
No worries.

649
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,640
现在你要纹多少
How much more you want to do right now?

650
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:58,820
填满这一块吗
Fill in this area?

651
00:33:58,820 --> 00:34:01,400
嗯  然后下面再多加一个罂粟
Yeah. And, uh, one more poppy down here.

652
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:02,550
一次做这么多啊
That's a lot for one sitting.

653
00:34:02,860 --> 00:34:03,660
我知道
I know.

654
00:34:04,350 --> 00:34:05,180
好吧
Okay.

655
00:34:37,700 --> 00:34:38,770
弗兰西斯
Francis?

656
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:49,050
这就走吗
You're heading in?

657
00:34:49,210 --> 00:34:51,250
门多萨起的早
Mendoza's an early riser.

658
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:53,940
你会解决好的
You'll figure this out.

659
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:57,350
我得证明副总统不是吃素的
I need to prove what the Vice President is capable of.

660
00:34:57,580 --> 00:35:00,070
别向他们证明  向我证明
Don't prove it to them. Prove it to me.

661
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:06,960
柯蒂斯抓着我的要害  弗兰克
Curtis has me by the tea bags, Frank.

662
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,440
没他我的党派就要乱套
I don't have a working majority without him.

663
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:10,090
可他不是多数党领袖
He wasn't elected leader.

664
00:35:10,090 --> 00:35:12,100
是没错  但我也得选边站
True. But I have to pick my battles.

665
00:35:12,100 --> 00:35:13,950
你要是在预算问题上无法控制他
If you can't control him on budgetary issues --

666
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:16,950
不光是他  还有听命于他的15个参议员
It's not just him. It's the 15 senators he has under his thumb.

667
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:18,800
没他们支持我就不能连任
I won't be the leader next year if they turn on me.

668
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,620
他想我们求他  把他找来
So he wants to be courted. Sit him down --

669
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:22,680
我试过和他谈了  但他不肯让步
I already tried talking to him. He wouldn't budge.

670
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:23,800
那我们一起去跟他谈
Then we'll both talk to him.

671
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,870
他已经表明立场了
He's made his position clear.

672
00:35:24,870 --> 00:35:27,060
我们都在这张桌子旁握手了
We all shook hands at this table.

673
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:28,540
我最多只能保证限制替代修正案
The most I can do is put the substitute amendment

674
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:30,280
表决前的辩论
on the floor with limited debate.

675
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:32,940
你们那边公开怎么说随你们便
Now, your people can say whatever they want for the record.

676
00:35:33,290 --> 00:35:34,620
但我们会投票否决修正案
But we're gonna vote the amendment down.

677
00:35:34,620 --> 00:35:37,790
我对象征性姿态不敢兴趣
I am not interested in symbolic gestures.

678
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:40,950
我只能做到这样
That's all I can offer.

679
00:35:41,950 --> 00:35:43,290
你的勇气哪去了
Where's your courage?

680
00:35:44,120 --> 00:35:46,850
我权力有限  弗兰克
My power has limits, Frank.

681
00:35:46,930 --> 00:35:48,940
再有五个共和党人  你那票就定胜负了
Five Republicans makes you the deciding vote.

682
00:35:46,930 --> 00:35:48,940
{\an8}参议院投票打平时  作为参议院主席的副总统才能投出决定票

683
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:50,380
现在很难说
Now, it's highly doubtful

684
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,910
我们能不能让他们违反党派意志投票
we can get them to vote against their own party.

685
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,490
但他们可以弃权
But they might abstain.

686
00:35:53,490 --> 00:35:54,330
那需要10人弃权
You'd need 10.

687
00:35:54,330 --> 00:35:56,160
福利改革是共和党人的长期追求
Entitlement is the Republicans' white whale.

688
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:57,760
我至少能说通两个人
I can get at least two of 'em to flip.

689
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,500
那就只需要六票弃权
And you'd only need six abstaining.

690
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,810
艾瑞克森已经在打电话了
Erikson's already making calls.

691
00:36:00,810 --> 00:36:01,560
唐纳
Donner?

692
00:36:01,570 --> 00:36:02,290
还有普拉斯科
And Pulaski.

693
00:36:02,290 --> 00:36:04,510
给我一份名单  我跟他一起上阵
All right. Get me a call list so I can tag-team with him.

694
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,540
在这儿
Got it right here.

695
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,820
我们得使狠招
We have to get medieval.

696
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:09,180
要说议院程序
When it comes to parliamentary procedure,

697
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:10,690
没有哪条规定我不知道  先生
there's not a rule I don't know, sir.

698
00:36:10,690 --> 00:36:12,420
给我找到能钻空子的
Find me the ones we can bend.

699
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:15,710
马克  你是个明白人
Mark, you're a sensible man.

700
00:36:16,850 --> 00:36:21,080
是  我知道  我懂
Yes, I -- I know -- I understand.

701
00:36:22,270 --> 00:36:24,910
如果  跟你说
What if -- tell you what.

702
00:36:24,910 --> 00:36:28,590
如果你选区内的两家退伍军人医院  对  两家
What if both VA hospitals in your district -- yes, both of them.

703
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:30,040
别挂  谁
Hold on. Who?

704
00:36:30,050 --> 00:36:30,660
莫里亚蒂
Moriarty.

705
00:36:30,660 --> 00:36:33,190
我答应给他的牲牛研究中心拨款
I promised him an amendment for his bovine research center.

706
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,010
这就有六票了
That makes six.

707
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:36,310
马克  如果我能给两家医院提供资金
Mark, if I can get you funding for both,

708
00:36:36,310 --> 00:36:37,810
你愿跟我们合作吗
are you with us?

709
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:40,150
非常好
Excellent.

710
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:40,980
你这几天来白宫
You come by the White House

711
00:36:40,980 --> 00:36:42,800
跟我共进午餐吧
and have lunch with me sometime soon.

712
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,900
再见  数目够了
Bye-bye. We have the numbers.

713
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,420
你打断点名之后
Once you break the quorum call

714
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:47,520
会有些麻烦
it's gonna be a little tricky.

715
